liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: Stokes is out! That's a great ball from Mitch Starc! Straight, good length, angling away a touch and hitting the top of off stump. Stokes has played all around it, looking to turn the ball into the leg side and it's made an awful mess of the off stump. Stokes goes for 3 off 16.
